<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head><meta charset="utf-8"><title>{{if .IsFinalAttempt}}Final notice — payment failed{{else}}Payment failed{{end}}</title></head>
<body style="font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,sans-serif;background:#141414;color:#eee;margin:0;padding:24px;">
  <div style="max-width:520px;margin:0 auto;background:#1f1f1f;padding:32px;border-radius:8px;">
    <h1 style="color:#FF6700;margin:0 0 16px;font-size:22px;">{{if .IsFinalAttempt}}Final notice — payment failed{{else}}Payment failed{{end}}</h1>
    <p style="margin:0 0 16px;line-height:1.5;">Hi {{.Name}},</p>
    {{- if .IsFinalAttempt}}
    <p style="margin:0 0 16px;line-height:1.5;">your charge for the <strong>{{.PlanName}}</strong> plan ({{.Amount}}) failed on the final retry. Your subscription will be paused and your workspace downgraded to the free tier shortly.</p>
    <p style="margin:0 0 16px;line-height:1.5;">Your data stays put. Update your payment method to restore the {{.PlanName}} plan:</p>
    {{- else}}
    <p style="margin:0 0 16px;line-height:1.5;">your charge for the <strong>{{.PlanName}}</strong> plan ({{.Amount}}) didn't go through{{if gt .AttemptCount 1}} (attempt {{.AttemptCount}}){{end}}. We'll try again on <strong>{{.RetryDate}}</strong>.</p>
    <p style="margin:0 0 16px;line-height:1.5;">To keep your workspace active, please update your payment method:</p>
    {{- end}}
    <p style="margin:24px 0;">
      <a href="{{.BillingURL}}" style="background:#FF6700;color:#fff;padding:12px 24px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;">Update payment method</a>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0 0 16px;line-height:1.5;color:#aaa;font-size:13px;">Or if you'd rather retry now: <a href="{{.RetryURL}}" style="color:#FF6700;">retry charge now</a>.</p>
    {{- if not .IsFinalAttempt}}
    <p style="margin:24px 0 0;line-height:1.5;color:#aaa;font-size:13px;">If the charge keeps failing we'll pause the plan for now &mdash; but your data stays put.</p>
    {{- end}}
  </div>
</body>
</html>
